{
  "id": "69c30434da960f7825cc0313",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:ガスライティング",
  "created": 1774388297,
  "updated": 1774388315,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c30434da960f7825cc0313",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:ガスライティング",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388297,
      "updated": 1774388297
    },
    {
      "id": "69c30449000000000081a838",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388297,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a839",
      "text": "はいはーい！今日のテーマは「[ガスライティング]」ね〜。なんか名前だけ聞くと、炎属性の魔法っぽくない？w",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83c",
      "text": "（微笑）確かに、どこか幻想的な響きがございますね。けれど、その実態は少々…人の心に影を落とすような現象でございます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a83f",
      "text": "炎属性ではない。心理操作の一種。簡潔に言うと、「相手の認識や記憶を疑わせることで支配する行為」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a840",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a841",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a842",
      "text": "うわ、それメンタル版バグらせ攻撃じゃん…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a843",
      "text": "「え、それ言ってないよ？」とか「気のせいじゃない？」みたいなやつでしょ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a844",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a845",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a846",
      "text": "正確。その積み重ねで、被害者は自己認識に不信を持つ。結果、加害者への依存が強まる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a847",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a848",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a849",
      "text": "なんとも…静かに、しかし確実に心を蝕むようで、胸が痛みますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84a",
      "text": "まるで、自分の記憶という灯火を、少しずつ吹き消されていくような…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84d",
      "text": "うわ、その例えエモいけど怖っ…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84e",
      "text": "でもさ、これってさ、やってる側ってわざとなの？それとも無意識パターンもある？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a84f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a850",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a851",
      "text": "両方ある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a852",
      "text": "意図的なケースは「コントロール目的」。無意識の場合は、自己防衛や認知の歪みが原因。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a853",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a854",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a855",
      "text": "つまり、その方自身もまた、心のどこかで歪みを抱えている可能性があるのですね…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a856",
      "text": "（少し考える）ただ、それが他者を傷つける理由にはなりませんけれど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a857",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a858",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a859",
      "text": "それな〜。理由があっても被害は消えないし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85a",
      "text": "てかさ、これって気づきにくくない？なんかじわじわ来る系じゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85d",
      "text": "そこが問題点。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85e",
      "text": "チェックポイントとしては、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a85f",
      "text": " 自分の記憶に過剰に自信が持てなくなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a860",
      "text": " 頻繁に謝罪してしまう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a861",
      "text": " 「自分が悪い」と感じやすくなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a862",
      "text": "などがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a863",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a864",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a865",
      "text": "あー、それ「デバフかかってる状態」って感じだね…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a866",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a867",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a868",
      "text": "（微笑）ふーこさんの表現は、いつも現代的で分かりやすいですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a869",
      "text": "まるでゲームの状態異常のように、知らぬ間に心が弱っていく…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86c",
      "text": "状態異常：混乱＋自己疑念デバフ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86d",
      "text": "回復アイテムは「第三者の視点」と「記録」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a86f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a870",
      "text": "記録って、メモとか？スクショとか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a871",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a872",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a873",
      "text": "その通り。会話のログ、日記など。客観的証拠になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a874",
      "text": "あと、信頼できる人に共有することも有効。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a875",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a876",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a877",
      "text": "誰かに話すことで、自分の感じた違和感が確かなものだと確認できるのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a878",
      "text": "孤独の中では、不安はより深く根を張りますから…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a879",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87b",
      "text": "なるほどね〜。一人で抱え込むと詰むやつだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87c",
      "text": "てかさ、りかって急に「回復アイテム」とか言うのじわるんだけどw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a87f",
      "text": "…比喩は必要。ユーザビリティ向上のため。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a880",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a881",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a882",
      "text": "（くすっと笑う）りかさんの中にも、遊び心が垣間見えますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a883",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a884",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a885",
      "text": "まとめると〜、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a886",
      "text": "ガスライティング＝「相手の頭をバグらせて支配するやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a887",
      "text": "対策＝「ログ取る・人に相談・自分の感覚を大事に」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a888",
      "text": "って感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a889",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88b",
      "text": "概ね正しい。要点を再掲：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88c",
      "text": " 1. ガスライティングは心理的操作",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88d",
      "text": " 2. 自己認識を揺らすのが目的",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88e",
      "text": " 3. 記録と第三者視点が対抗策",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a88f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a890",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a891",
      "text": "大切なのは、自分の感じた違和感を、無理に押し込めないことかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a892",
      "text": "小さな声でも、それは確かに心からの訴えなのですから…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a893",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a894",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a895",
      "text": "うんうん、それな！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a896",
      "text": "「なんかおかしい」って思ったら、それフラグだからね〜。スルーしないの大事！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a897",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a898",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a899",
      "text": "フラグ回収は慎重に。バッドエンド回避のために。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89b",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89c",
      "text": "（微笑）まるで人生が一冊の物語のようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89d",
      "text": "できることなら、穏やかな結末へと進みたいものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a89f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a8a0",
      "text": "よし！今日はちょっと真面目回だったけど、いい感じにまとまったね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3044a000000000081a8a1",
      "text": "次はもっとゆるいテーマにしよ〜w",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388299,
      "updated": 1774388299
    },
    {
      "id": "69c30450000000000081a8a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774388304,
      "updated": 1774388304
    },
